metadata.title: Paper Towel Holder, Wooden Kitchen Roll Stand Organizer Free Standing, Housewarming Gift Present for Friends
features: [Simple and Natural] This paper towel holder is with flower design and made from beech, super cute and beautiful natural wood color, looks attractive on the counter.
[Lightweight but Sturdy] This wooden holder stands 14.37inch/36.5cm tall and weights 370g, the rod is 11.4inch/29cm, lightweight but sturdy enough.

[Easy to install] Easy to assemble, you just twist the rod into the base no tools needed. It took less than a minute to put together. This holder will be arrived in three pieces, the screws are protected well by black cap, no need to worry about it won't screw together.

The holder's base is with 5.12inch/13cm length, 5.12inch/13cm width and 0.79inch/2cm height, a rubber strip at the bottom to stop it from sliding. The wooden pole sits firmly on the base and is very stable.
[Practical Kitchen Accessory] This is a kitchen essential if you use kitchen roll, , great for the kitchen work surface to keep the kitchen roll handy and nearby.
[Multi-use product] Great for your kitchen and bathroom, you may conjure up many other uses for this, like to hold your large balls of wool, to hold your rolls of tape, etc.
Easy to clean with no annoying nooks or crannies.
